&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dynamic and results-driven Corporate Sales Specialist to drive revenue growth across Mejuri’s Corporate Sales and Events channel. This role will focus on sourcing new opportunities, booking corporate events, and managing relationships that generate incremental revenue through private shopping events and bulk corporate gifting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for identifying and pursuing new business opportunities, managing inbound and outbound leads, and converting them into booked events and bulk orders. This role will work closely with retail teams to ensure successful event execution while owning the revenue target for the corporate sales channel.&lt;/p&gt;
