&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development &amp;amp; Pipeline Generation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively source and pursue new corporate event and gifting opportunities through outbound outreach, referrals, and partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage a pipeline of qualified corporate clients interested in private shopping events and bulk gifting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Convert leads into booked events and corporate orders to drive revenue growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Event Bookings &amp;amp; Coordination&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the client-facing booking process for private events and corporate gifting opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collect and share necessary event details with store teams to ensure smooth execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support clients in selecting the appropriate event or gifting format for their needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Corporate Sales&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive revenue through corporate gifting, bulk orders, and private shopping events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present corporate packages, pricing, and promotions to prospective clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track opportunities and bookings within CRM systems (Hubspot)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Relationship Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain strong relationships with corporate clients and partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary point of contact for clients throughout the booking process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify repeat opportunities and referrals within existing accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting &amp;amp; Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track pipeline activity, bookings, and revenue performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate records in CRM and ensure proper handoff of event details to internal teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide regular updates on pipeline health and upcoming events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
